headline: RETURN TO SENDER: AZ Gov Candidate Kari Lake Says Send Migrant Buses Back Across the Border
author: The First
sentences: “I think it’s really cute that some of these governors are putting the illegal aliens on the buses and shipping them to Delaware or D.C. —but they still remain our problem when that’s happening.
Arizona gubernatorial candidate Kari Lake says busing migrants to D.C. doesn’t solve the problem —we have to send them back across the border.

We have to send these buses back to the border and unload them back across the border,” Lake says
